
1. visit http://alchim31.free.fr/m2e-scala/update-site/ 
   download zip 
   put "features" and "plugins" in your eclipse folder "eclipse/dropins/Scala/" 
   restart eclipse 
   new scala project 
   
2. pom import 
   <dependency>
    <groupId>org.apache.spark</groupId>
    <artifactId>spark-core_2.11</artifactId>
    <version>2.2.1</version>
  </dependency>
  
3. easy demo for scala spark
  